of spectral densities or entropy. We thus predict\nthat future advances in cosmological observations and collider technology will\nsandwich from above and below, and eventually discover, new (non-perturbative)\nphysics beyond the Standard Model within the TeV-PeV energy range.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Mar 2015 20:00:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 4 Jul 2015 13:55:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2016 22:13:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-06"}
