 the case that the magnetic field in the Perseus arm is lifted up from the\nplane towards high latitudes. The magnetic field strength and the electron\ndensity we derived for the W4 superbubble are important parameters for\nevolution models of superbubbles breaking out of the Galactic plane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Apr 2015 08:31:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
